{"tid":486831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴車長呃病假　秘撈駕小巴","createTime":"2017-12-02T07:51:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T09:46:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2f42a5eda6e5c80913a7d147b4f9230f9c545424","tid":486831,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T07:51:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171202/20232286\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171202%2F20232286&d=ZnPwUJ5vcJDBIEOVVy4YbS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=1235d2bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171202%2F20232286&h=9d1dc3bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171202/20232286</a><br />\n<br />\n九巴車長呃病假　秘撈駕小巴<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171202/large/a03a01a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171202%2Flarge%2Fa03a01a.gif&h=de12cc4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九巴人員「放蛇」時發現涉事車長駕駛時手部靈活，不似受傷。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名九巴車長涉向公司呃假3個月，聲稱被車長駕駛室的閘門夾傷右手中指至骨裂，報稱不能駕駛，工傷後一直休假，每月按法例繼續支取五分四的月薪。他日前被揭在休假期間駕綠色小巴「秘撈」，九巴報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n九巴派員放蛇拍片<br />\n<br />\n涉騙取工傷假的司機姓賴，46歲，加入九巴18年。據悉，今年8月23日他向九巴報稱當日休息期間，他登上另一輛巴士與同事閒聊時，右手中指被駕駛室閘門夾傷骨裂影響手部活動不能駕駛，遂向公司申報工傷，並提供醫生紙申領病假，惟醫生紙上只列明他中指受傷。<br />\n<br />\n賴持續申請工傷病假，三度向公司提交醫生紙，其病假至今年12月25日。據了解，九巴日前收到有人舉報，指賴沒有上班3個月期間任職綠色專線小巴司機，駕駛52K線。九巴翌日派員調查，又「放蛇」登上賴駕駛的小巴，並拍下證據，發現賴駕駛時手部靈活，操控自如。職員其後上前表明身份，賴對虛報工傷直認不諱。九巴及後解僱車長並報警。<br />\n<br />\n■記者唐靄琳"},{"pid":"352a6780cc88e23d634d05e56a841fc8309f9197","tid":486831,"uid":75765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T08:00:26.000Z","msg":"揸綠van唔駛用中指"},{"pid":"d8c3b5d08e37f0cc519e094cadc5e7d828e0734b","tid":486831,"uid":101396,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T08:36:07.000Z","msg":"擺明被人篤灰啦"},{"pid":"1bebfe47d5e8c83c11d25773dbc9efbd3ee7ada9","tid":486831,"uid":127075,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T08:46:43.000Z","msg":"條友性賴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n賴得就賴"},{"pid":"643ce193597f4c12ed155cff9a1261531e0e0f5e","tid":486831,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T08:54:08.000Z","msg":"鍾意自己份事業都有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f0dfbe7546375416249792fb37e9141d8be095","tid":486831,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:03:51.000Z","msg":"其實報工傷如果請長假保險公司通常都會搵私家偵探查啦"},{"pid":"f6670bc0b030729d8e7b0e38d9bc146c500c0d4a","tid":486831,"uid":16767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:05:17.000Z","msg":"九巴日前收到有人舉報<br />\n<br />\n好朋友"},{"pid":"bdd565f564d785f21dfe858d118e8327ddfb9804","tid":486831,"uid":45591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:07:25.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"94dc10574be6ddc03ff7cb286923aaaad9abcbd5","tid":486831,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 醫生使唔使告埋？"}]}